        'In Outlook on the Web, click New Email and use Copilot to draft an internal email to the team immediately after the Technology Steering Committee, summarising the key decisions, the expectations for Red-status areas, and the rules for external communications until approved messaging is issued. Reference the playbook and the brand documents for the disclosure restrictions. End with 3 bullet points titled "What you must do today". Use Coach my response to keep the tone firm and aligned.'
